HEADWORD: Gemmeous
<hw>Gem"me*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>gemmeus</ets>. See <er>Gem</er>.]</ety> <def>Pertaining to gems; of
